Elk Grove

Overview

Qualifications
We went undefeated until the last match, which was against the other undefeated team. We lost the match due to field control issues, pushing us down to second seed.

Eliminations
We spent a long time considering what an ideal alliance partner would look like. Ultimately we decided that a robot that could push goals up the ramp would complement us the most. That asset combined with our observations of Acme Robotics' (Team 8367) speed and impressive goal-pushing capability led us to decide to choose them over accepting an invitation from first seed, Capitals (Team 7464). We went undefeated in finals.

Awards

  • Winning Alliance Captain
  • Won PTC Design
  • Won Inspire 3rd Place
  • Nominated for Think
  • Nominated for Innovate
  • Nominated for Control
